          Web development is the act of creating pieces of software for the "web", or the internet.
          According to <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_development"> this wikipedia article, </a>
         web development is the work involved in developing a web site for the Internet (World Wide Web) or an intranet (a private network). 
        </p>

